events.name: Tampa Bay Buccaneers at Chicago Bears

headlines.description: Nick Foles beat Tom Brady again, Cairo Santos kicked a 38-yard field with 1:17 left and the Chicago Bears beat Tampa Bay 20-19 on Thursday night after Brady seemingly lost count of downs on his final play.
headlines.shortLinkText: Foles beat Brady again as Bears squeeze by Tampa Bay 20-19
